title: BIG FACTS LIVE feat. YOUNG NUDY

description:
BIG FACTS PODCAST recently went live at the BUCKHEAD THEATRE in Atlanta. Hear Bank, Scream and Jade chop it up amongst themselves and a live studio audience.

YOUNG NUDY also joins them to discuss his new project, the streets and so much more.
